# Authentication system flow 

## Email OTP-Based Registration Flow
User в†’ Register (email, password)
   в†“
Create User (isVerified = false)
   в†“
Generate OTP (store hashed)
   в†“
Send Email OTP
   в†“
User enters OTP
   в†“
Verify OTP
   в†“
Activate Account (isVerified = true)
   в†“
Generate Access + Refresh Token
   в†“
User LoggedIn 

## Google OAuth Login Flow

User в†’ Click "Login with Google"
   в†“
Frontend gets Google ID Token
   в†“
Backend verifies token (Google API)
   в†“
Check user in DB
   в†“
IF exists в†’ Login
ELSE в†’ Create new user (isVerified = true)
   в†“
Generate Access + Refresh Token
   в†“
User Logged In 

## Manual Login Authentication Flow

User в†’ Enter email + password
   в†“
Find user
   в†“
Check password (bcrypt compare)
   в†“
Check isVerified
   в†“
Generate tokens
   в†“
Login success 

## Forgot Password Flow

User в†’ "Forgot Password"
   в†“
Enter email
   в†“
Generate OTP
   в†“
Send OTP
   в†“
User enters OTP
   в†“
Verify OTP
   в†“
Allow password reset
   в†“
Update password (hashed)
   в†“
Invalidate all sessions
   в†“
Login again 

